headline.main: Families Aim to Raise $15 Million to Search for Flight 370
headline.print_headline: Families Aim to Raise $15 Million to Search for Flight 370

lead_paragraph: The Philippine defense chief and two other Cabinet members on Saturday toured a U.S. aircraft carrier patrolling the disputed South China Sea on the invitation of the Navy, U.S. Embassy officials said.
